---
title: Pork Shawarma with Lemon Bulgur, Red Cabbage Slaw and Tahini Sauce
description: This disassembled classic Middle Eastern wrap is equally tasty and colourful! Our Shawarma blend is smoky, sweet and oh so delicious. Paired with seasoned onions, crunchy cabbage, veggie packed bulgur and drizzled with tangy tahini dressing.
